---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
	title="About Us"
	description="Learn about Sonia Buddy - West Bengal's trusted platform for bus timetables and vehicle rental services."
>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>About Sonia Buddy</h1>
			<p>Your trusted travel companion in West Bengal</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="card">
				<h2>Who We Are</h2>
				<p>Sonia Buddy is a West Bengal-based travel service platform dedicated to making transportation information accessible and convenient for everyone. We specialize in providing bus timetable information and vehicle rental services across the state.</p>
				<p>Our platform connects travelers with essential travel information and service providers, helping you plan your journeys efficiently. Whether you need to check bus schedules between cities or find a reliable vehicle rental with driver, Sonia Buddy is here to assist you.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="card">
				<h2>Our Mission</h2>
				<p>To simplify travel planning in West Bengal by providing accurate, up-to-date bus timetables and connecting people with reliable vehicle rental services. We believe that access to transportation information should be easy, fast, and available to everyone.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="card">
				<h2>What We Offer</h2>
				<h3>Bus Timetable Search</h3>
				<p>Find bus schedules and timings between cities across West Bengal. Our comprehensive database includes information about departure times, arrival times, bus types, and routes for major destinations including Kolkata, Siliguri, Durgapur, Asansol, Burdwan, and more.</p>
				
				<h3>Vehicle Rental Services</h3>
				<p>Connect with vehicle rental providers offering cars, buses, toto, pickup vans, and ambulances with professional drivers. Whether you need a vehicle for personal travel, group tours, goods transport, or medical emergencies, we help you find the right option.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="card">
				<h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Local Expertise:</strong> We understand West Bengal's transportation network and local needs</li>
					<li><strong>Comprehensive Coverage:</strong> Bus routes and vehicle rentals across the state</li>
					<li><strong>User-Friendly:</strong> Simple, fast, and accessible platform</li>
					<li><strong>Reliable Information:</strong> Accurate and up-to-date travel data</li>
					<li><strong>No Hidden Fees:</strong> Transparent pricing and information</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="card">
				<h2>Our Coverage Area</h2>
				<p>We currently serve major cities and regions across West Bengal including:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Kolkata and surrounding areas</li>
					<li>Siliguri and North Bengal region</li>
					<li>Durgapur and Asansol industrial belt</li>
					<li>Burdwan and Bardhaman district</li>
					<li>Darjeeling and hill stations</li>
					<li>And expanding to more locations</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="card">
				<h2>Contact Us</h2>
				<p>Have questions or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you. Visit our <a href="/contact">contact page</a> to get in touch with our team.</p>
				<a href="/contact" class="btn">Contact Us</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
